{"tid":1361354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］我係前線記者，我都有d野想講","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:59:40.000Z","uid":265443,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"819e2b15b0031c6a015314de933ea9bd5e220bd6","tid":1361354,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"就係我唔係記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦都冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你地出面個個差唔多成萬個正評嘅post<br />\n基本上就係係度blame前線有咩做得唔好點點點<br />\n人地一句話自己係記者係就信？<br />\n大佬呀駛唔駛簽到打卡印埋手印先去衝呀？<br />\n記者駛鬼你保護，話我冷血都係咁話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcc6d4fb934ffba6f41f69f8fbdb18b879c4948","tid":1361354,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62d22ab4a2062cad608c1f84878b7485d086f8ca","tid":1361354,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c20d9d60e2ae9784541d20fb35bcbe5ea692b999","tid":1361354,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17dfe57e84ac57c0d110128ce4b552e7f6720a30","tid":1361354,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\n不過落場同事後檢討係兩回事<br />\n唔使太認真"},{"pid":"f83f99c2754b21c3e0d66247fef34d43ba5c3b22","tid":1361354,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7795822978e7aacdccd2d7a07efe42094327d102","tid":1361354,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dccaf5d63a467a5f5ce99831aef9b5301cb292ee","tid":1361354,"uid":2